HEADWORD: Seagoing
<hw>Sea"go`ing</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Going upon the sea;
especially, sailing upon the deep sea; -- used in distinction from
<xex>coasting</xex> or <xex>river</xex>, as applied to
vessels.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

